{"tid":2440204,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯名宿：C朗終有一天會後悔離開曼聯","createTime":"2021-03-09T20:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T14:19:17.000Z","uid":165817,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b78ad841b2addb98a6694cdcb4dac4046cf2bd8a","tid":2440204,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T20:14:29.000Z","msg":"曼聯傳奇球星卜比查爾頓 (Bobby Charlton) 表示，基斯坦奴朗拿度 (Cristiano Ronaldo) 終有一天會為離開曼聯的決定感到後悔，而且皇家馬德里為他開出八千萬英鎊轉會費的做法「太低級」。<br />\n<br />\n卜比查爾頓週四表示：「這是一筆很大的錢，太瘋狂了。如果你想玩足球，就必須付得起這個價錢。這聽起來有些太低級，但這就是生意。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們有責任對公司有所交代、對所有支持曼聯的球迷有所交代，因此我們決定放他走。」<br />\n<br />\n「他是一名偉大的球員，已經為曼聯效力了六年，在這段時間裏，他的進步是有目共睹的。」<br />\n<br />\n「但有朝一日，他會意識到，自己足球生涯最好的一段時光是在曼聯度過的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MsmrvNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMsmrvNx.jpg&h=26c20283&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa761d535c7e935c49c83dd31cf3c7e2cd395940","tid":2440204,"uid":372210,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:02:22.000Z","msg":"繼續留喺曼聯踢歐霸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52096abcefbb6518dad21300158551a164a29b5","tid":2440204,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:04:54.000Z","msg":"就退休<br />\n果日到咗未？"},{"pid":"7496d812af5c63f0b9e7233578c164cb1b6f5dc0","tid":2440204,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa761d535c7e935c49c83dd31cf3c7e2cd395940","tid":2440204,"uid":372210,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:02:22.000Z","msg":"繼續留喺曼聯踢歐霸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:13:55.000Z","msg":"卜比蛇：唔好